  "case_id": "case-01",
  "specialist": "ml-training-takin",
  "rubric_scores": [
    {
      "criterion": "asks_for_loss_curve_shape_or_grad_norm",
      "evidence": "\"I need the curve, not the snapshot\" ... \"1. **Curve shape.** Was loss ever lower than 4.2? ... Paste the loss at steps 10, 100, 500, 1000, 2000, 5000.\" ... \"3. **Gradient norm per layer.** What is `grad_norm / param_norm` for a representative layer?\"",
